description: Studentbostäder i Sverige AB owns, manages, and develops student housing facilities. The company is headquartered in Uppsala, Uppsala and currently employs 21 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-12-18. The firm offers student housing and a fully digitalized rental management in eleven university cities all across Sweden.
